name: The world in the hands of metaverse people

metadata.name: The world in the hands of metaverse people
metadata.description:
In today's world, Metaverse people have the most income from their art and thought.
In the digital world, we earn by thinking and innate talents.
The day will come when global trade is in the hands of crypto-currencies and digital metaverse.
And that day is very near.
By buying from us, help us in our mission, which is to help the needy.
